This is the homeassistant yaml for the VPmonitor 1.2 for ivt490, vers 1.2 has additional control functions for GTE5 & EXT IN


This code is based on https://github.com/stefanh12/IVT_490_esphome with adaption for this HW platform.

See WIKI for more info on status on this project https://github.com/uabpra/ivt490/wiki/IVT490-monitor

